premise_source_doc_sentence: Terminator Genisys is a 2015 American science fiction action film directed by Alan Taylor and written by Laeta Kalogridis and Patrick Lussier .
The events of the game take place in the post-apocalyptic universe of the Terminator Genisys film .
She is one of the main protagonists of The Terminator , Terminator 2 : Judgment Day and Terminator Genisys , as well as the television series Terminator : The Sarah Connor Chronicles .

Sarah was portrayed by Linda Hamilton in The Terminator and Terminator 2 : Judgment Day , by Lena Headey in Terminator : The Sarah Connor Chronicles , and by Emilia Clarke and Willa Taylor in Terminator Genisys .

A shapeshifting android assassin , the T-1000 is the main antagonist of Terminator 2 : Judgment Day , as well as a supporting antagonist in Terminator 2 : 3-D Battle Across Time and Terminator Genisys .
